videos.description: Brandon Goodwin gets on the ground to save a steal and finds John Collins, who throws down the emphatic dunk.

videos.description: Off a Knicks turnover, Trae Young speeds down the court and lobs it up to Clint Capela, who throws down the dunk.

videos.headline: Trae, Capela connect for alley-oop in transition

videos.description: Julius Randle finds Kevin Knox II in the corner and he pulls up to nail the 3-pointer as the buzzer sounds, cutting the Hawks' lead to four.
